@UBL neocortex-skills
LEXICO: #skills #neocortex
## Skills NeoCortex (.opencode/skills/)

| Skill | Regra | Pipeline |
|---|---|---|
| **nc-validate** | R6 | ruff + mypy + py_compile + bandit + yaml + mdc + json + @LOCKS + secret |
| **nc-lint** | R6 | ruff check + ruff format + mypy (rapido) |
| **nc-audit** | R17 | Auditoria 3 camadas FR-173 + compliance report |
| **nc-handoff** | R12 | Gera NC-DS-*-handoff-*.yaml |
| **nc-boot-sync** | R16 | Sincroniza @BOOT + catalog refresh |
| **nc-ssot-update** | R02 | Atualiza @SSOT com changelog |





